channel.description:
create a new text document and name it news.txt

Open client.java

Declare This:
[code]String[] news = getNews();[/code]

Then Find:
[code]public static void main(String args[])[/code]

And above it should be a method something like this:

[code]public static final void method52(boolean flag)[/code]
then add this above that

[code]	public static String[] getNews() {
		try {
			URL newsUrl = new URL("http://your.website/news.txt");
			BufferedReader reader = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(
					newsUrl.openStream()));
			String news = "";
			String buffer;
			while ((buffer = reader.readLine()) != null) news += buffer + "\n";
System.out.println(news);
			return news.split("\n");
		} catch (Exception e) {
			System.out.println("Error obtaining news.");
			e.printStackTrace();
			return new String[]{"Error obtaining news."};
		}
	}
[/code]

Remember to edit
[code]URL newsUrl = new URL("http://your.website/news.txt");[/code]

then upload news.txt to your website
